==Indonesian==
===Noun===
'''kakak'''

# [[older]] [[brother]]/[[sister]], older [[sibling]]
# older [[cousin]]
# term of address for a friend who is a bit older

====Usage====
* "Kakak [[laki-laki]]" is used to mean "older brother".
* "Kakak [[perempuan]]" is used to mean "older sister".

